Feature: User Valid Login
  As a registered user
  I want to sign in to the application
  So that I can access the user dashboard

  Background:
    Given the login page is displayed

  Scenario: Successful login with valid credentials
    When I enter the valid username 'user'
    And I enter the valid password 'pass'
    And I click the 'Sign In' button
    Then I should be able to observe the user dashboard
;
Feature: Create Customer Satisfaction Survey
  As a signed-in user
  I want to create a new Customer Satisfaction Survey
  So that users will be able to create questions

  Background:
    Given I am signed in
    And I can see my dashboard

  Scenario: Create a new Customer Satisfaction Survey
    When I navigate to the Odontologist project
    And I select to add a new question set
    And I set the survey title to 'Customer Satisfaction Survey'
    And I set the survey ID to 'satisfaction1'
    And I set the description to 'This is a Customer Satisfaction Survey'
    And I click the 'Continue' button
    Then the 'Customer Satisfaction Survey' should be created
    And the question set editor should be displayed
